<!--
	=====================================================================================
	TEXTURE ATLAS FILE
	Defines example texture atlas definitions.
	=====================================================================================
	A texture atlas file for Tetragon contains one or more TextureAtlas sections, each
	for a related texture image that contains graphics that are being used for the atlas.
	The format is similar to that of the Sparrow/Starling Texture Atlas format. The only
	differences are that the Tetragon Texture Atlas sections are inside the <data> tag
	and have an imageID attribute instead of an imagePath attribute.
	=====================================================================================
-->
